Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Answer
    An answer from the server to one of the client requests.
    Idea
    An idea submitted from one of the users.
    Participation
    A participation used to add a new person to the list of the people interested in an idea.
    Request
    A request to execute by the server.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    RequestType
    Enumeration of all the available requests: - ADD to add a new idea, - LIST_IDEA to list all ideas, - PARTICIPATE to add a participant to an idea, - LIST_INTEREST to list all the emails of the people interested in one idea.
